comments: Daniels (NOP) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Graham (NOP), who extends his foot and creates the marginal contact.
Jones (SAS) cleanly deflects the ball away from Murphy III (NOP) and any ensuing contact is incidental.
Daniels (NOP) reaches in and initiates illegal contact to Jones's (SAS) head near midcourt.
Jones (SAS) makes contact with the ball before the ensuing marginal contact with McCollum's (NOP) arm during the driving shot attempt.
Collins (SAS) initiates contact with Valanciunas' (NOP) arm and affects Valanciunas' ability to secure the rebound.
Branham (SAS) initiates illegal contact with Valanciunas' (NOP) arm, affecting his ability to secure the pass.
Jones (NOP) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making illegal contact with Graham (SAS).
Jones (NOP) firms up in a screening position in Champagnie's (SAS) path without delivering contact.
Champagnie (SAS) gets a hand on the ball before Jones's (NOP) shot attempt is cleanly blocked by Wembanyama (SAS).
Murphy III (NOP) commits a take foul on Graham (SAS).
Jones (NOP) establishes himself in Branham's (SAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
McCollum (NOP) jumps and returns to the floor before illegally starting his dribble.
Hawkins (NOP) commits a take foul on Wembanyama (SAS).
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that McCollum (NOP) released the shot attempt prior to the expiration of the game clock.
